    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini nostri Iehsu Christi Dei eterni, anno dominice
                        incarnationis millesimo septuagesimo nono, pridie idus junii. (…) Infra <rs
                            key="#Castle">castellum</rs> qod (sic) dicitur de <placeName
                            ref="#places/63" key="#Castle #Baptismal_churches">Sancta Maria ad
                            Monte</placeName> et prope ecclesiam et <rs key="#Baptismal_churches"
                            >plebem</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Baptismal_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/72">Sancte
                            Marie</orgName>, presentibus bonorum virorum quorum nomina supter
                        leguntur, <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName> rector
                        et ghubernator de <orgName key="#Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3203"
                                ><rs key="#Hospitals">hospitale</rs> qod vocatur Rosaia</orgName> in
                        magna penuria positus erat, quesivit et petit domno <persName key="#Bishops"
                                ><rs key="#Bishops">epischupo</rs>
                            <name ref="Anselmus">Anselmo</name></persName> ut pro caritate atque
                        substentatione pauperum peregrinorum leprosorumque (…) donaret atque
                        concederet firmando atque predicto hospitali medietatem <rs key="#Decima"
                            >decimarum</rs> que exerint (…) de illis terris novis que fuerunt de
                            <placeName key="#Decima" ref="#places/3209">Scleto</placeName>, de
                            <placeName key="#Decima" ref="#places/3247">Cerreto</placeName> et de
                            <placeName key="#Decima" ref="#places/3208">Cerbarya</placeName>, et
                        videntur esse de finibus atque <rs key="#Plebs">teritorio de predicta plebe
                        </rs>Sancte Marie atque de <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/614"
                            key="#Baptismal_churches"><rs key="#Baptismal_churches">plebe</rs> de
                                <placeName ref="#places/319">Cappiano</placeName></orgName> et de
                            <orgName key="#Baptismal_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3228"><rs
                                key="#Baptismal_churches">plebe</rs> de <placeName ref="#places/154"
                                key="#Baptismal_churches">Ripole</placeName></orgName>. (…)
                        Venerabilis epischopus Anselmus, suis annis inclinans, (…) concessit dedit
                        predicto hospitale de Rosaia medietates decimarum de nominatis terris in
                        perpetuum (…) atque suo anatemate stabile in perpetuum confirmavit ut nullus
                        suus successor in epischupatus (…) vel aliqua magna vel parva persona rumpat
                        vel diminuat aut subtrahat (…). Beatus Anselmus episcopus adveniens in
                        prefatum locum ad Sanctam Mariam ad Monte audiens atque recongnoscens pro
                        predicti Iohanni rectore supradicti hospitalis qualiter predicti medietates
                        decimarum a iamdicti domni Anselmo concesse fuerunt predicti hospitali
                        rogati ab eodem Iohannes pro caritate Dei, iterum donando concessit atque
                        stabilivit ut predicti hospitale in perpetuum habeat et teneat prefatas
                        medietates decimarum de iamdictis terris novis de Ischeto, de Cerreto et de
                        Cerbaria. (…) <persName key="#Judge"><name ref="Leo"
                            >Lionectus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex domni imperatoris</rs> interfui. SM dei <rs
                            key="#Witness">presenti</rs>: <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Gherardus">Giraldi</name></persName> filii quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Morectus">Moretti</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Hubertus">Uberti</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Wido">Guidi</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Mattus">Mattoni</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Hubertus">Uberti</name></persName>.</ab>
                </div>
